title: Hour 3 - Neil Paine (06-02-20)

description:
Neil Paine tells Dan that the 4 billion dollar loss that the MLB owners are claiming they will lose does not add up. Neil walks Dan thru a couple possible scenarios, but says the numbers just don't bring him to that 4 billion dollar number.
